OL,5, Rape complainants should be told       
OL,6, pre-recording evidence could harm their
OL,7, chances of securing a conviction at    
OL,8, trial, researchers say.                
OL,10,F"Special measures" allow them to be    
OL,11,Finterviewed and cross-examined before  
OL,12,Fthe trial and away from the defendant. 
OL,14,FBut a University College London study, 
OL,15,Fthe first of its kind, found 20% fewer 
OL,16,Frape convictions in such cases.        
OL,18,FSpecial measures, under Section 28 of  
OL,19,Fthe Youth Justice and Criminal Evidence
OL,20,FAct 1999, were introduced in 2016.     
